code: @Override public void registerBeanDefinitions(AnnotationMetadata importingClassMetadata, BeanDefinitionRegistry registry) {     if (!registry.containsBeanDefinition(BEAN_NAME)) {         GenericBeanDefinition beanDefinition = new GenericBeanDefinition().         beanDefinition.setBeanClass(DataSourceInitializerPostProcessor.class).         beanDefinition.setRole(BeanDefinition.ROLE_INFRASTRUCTURE).         // We don't need this one to be post processed otherwise it can cause a         // cascade of bean instantiation that we would rather avoid.         beanDefinition.setSynthetic(true).         registry.registerBeanDefinition(BEAN_NAME, beanDefinition).     } }
